.DT
add_random_desc
Disk World creator help
add_random_desc

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_random_desc -  This method is to add to the list of random descriptions that can be added to specific room types.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_random_desc(string types,
string description,
mixed items,
mixed item_desc)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^types%^RESET%^ - the string of ASCII character type(s) that this desc could apply to
%^BOLD%^items%^RESET%^ - add_item name(s) (identical to the 'shorts' parameter in add_item)
%^BOLD%^item_desc%^RESET%^ - a string, or array of strings giving the corresponding item desc
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/terrain_map/handler_base.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is to add to the list of random descriptions that can be added to
specific room types. A specific random sequence is used so that the randoms
won't vary over time.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_random_desc_limit, set_random_chat_limit, add_random_chat, add_item

.EP

